title: 99 Ways to Become Heroes by Beauty Masters
description: 99 Ways to Become Heroes by Beauty Masters Manhua I, Lu Chen, am the only son of the King Lu. I thought I could live a life of nourishment at night since I was born. Unfortunately, my talent was too high, which was hard to find in the past. Five beautiful masters fell from the sky to force me to practice, each with extraordinary strength, the master of a domain, the master of a holy land, the empress of a thousand ages, the supreme empress of the world of pills, the emperor of alchemy, plus a sticky little sister…The road to holy cultivation is too much for a man to bear! Bei Meinü Shifu Tiaojiao Cheng Sheng Di 99 Zhong Fangfa Read Spare Me, My Beauty Master Disciple of Angels 被美女师傅调教成圣的99种方法
